description:
IMMACULATE HOME WITH BAY VIEWS
This brand new home is located in a quiet court only 100 metres from the sandy shores of north facing bay beaches. With bay views from the balcony and immaculate presentation, this home is ready for you to move straight in and enjoy.
The lower level offers:
• two spacious carpeted bedrooms, one with built in robe and the second with a walk in robe;
• family/entertainment room which extends out into the rear yard;
• an additional room perfect for a study or home office;
• generous main bathroom with luxurious bath and shower;
• laundry with built in cabinetry and access to the yard;
• separate toilet; and
• internal access to the double lockup garage.
The upper level features:
• an impressive master bedroom with private balcony, expansive walk in robe and en-suite with dual basins. extra large shower and separate toilet;
• beautifully appointed kitchen with butler's pantry, freestanding 5 burner gas cooktop and electric oven and beautiful stone benches;
• spacious open plan dining and lounge area extending onto the rear undercover deck, offering tranquil bay views; and
• Additional bathroom.
The home features ducted and split system heating and cooling, solar panels, water tank and double remote lock up garage. The property has beautiful low maintenance landscaped gardens spread across a spacious 631sqm allotment.
Located at the end of a private cul de sac and a short 100m stroll to the beach, this property is the perfect family home or holiday getaway.
